{"tid":570282,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《火拼時速4》即將開拍","createTime":"2018-02-23T13:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T16:09:28.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d07943d7cfb00909b34f43ca869a074995249f9","tid":570282,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"基斯&middot;德加(Chris Tucker）透露《火拼時速4（Rush Hour 4）》已經在籌備中。<br />\n<br />\n基斯&middot;德加日前在一節目中宣佈了這個消息，他表示他和成龍都已經準備就緒，將回歸續集。&ldquo;已經在進行了。這會是一場終身難忘的&lsquo;尖峰時刻&rsquo;。成龍和我都已經做好準備，我們會讓大家不要忘記這部作品。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過目前德加暫未透露任何有關該項目的細節內容，無論是上映時間還是導演人選都還是個未知數。曾執導過前三部《火拼時速》的導演布雷特&middot;拉特能（Brett Ratner）由於性騷擾醜聞纏身，回歸的可能性微乎其微。<br />\n<br />\n去年，在成龍拒絕了幾部不同的劇本後，也暗示了有一部特別的作品已經萬事俱備，只等德加點頭加盟，看來他所指的便是《火拼時速4》。<br />\n<br />\n《火拼時速》三部曲分別在1998、2001和2007年上映，在全球範圍內獲得了超過8億美元的票房。"},{"pid":"cc15667e35691c825cd11622c2808d2d938508b0","tid":570282,"uid":53413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"個黑人<br />\n真係好撚好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ad5b70cc6cc77beec0a3bc80bea15e26680f6a","tid":570282,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"1,2唔錯<br />\n3已經變晒質連個黑鬼個體格都變晒肥左2個碼"},{"pid":"ab23260ed0e8e5926bd6db35355c085f86066d61","tid":570282,"uid":40493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dU4lYcN6zEY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdU4lYcN6zEY&d=ofe%2BmqYPOb1lq9GThGjE0k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a374fc93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dU4lYcN6zEY</a>"},{"pid":"02b9888c0ddfdba6129208e53059a7c054a98f3e","tid":570282,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"老野又出黎cap水"},{"pid":"b9ddb60bd9fdf9c87450b36a34185aa5bc03308a","tid":570282,"uid":103230,"like":4,"disl